Package: mplyr
Type: Package
Title: Matrix manipulation utilities
Version: 0.2
Date: 2015-03-04
Author: Giuseppe A. Paleologo
Maintainer: Giuseppe A. Paleologo <paleologo@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides functions for easier manipulation of
    n-dimensional arrays (n <= 6): subsetting, aggregation, alignment,
    accumulation. See README for more details.
